init_text:
What Are the Most Important Things Students Should Learn in School?

In your opinion, what are the most important things students should learn in school? What is the most important thing you have learned in school? How has this knowledge affected your life? How do you think it will help your success in the future?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think this is more important than learning facts in a textbook, or grades that are given based on it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's helped me succeed many times, such as when I needed to write an essay as well as lead a group presentation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Learning how to handle these situations is crucial to ones success in school as well as later on in life.
